WHO   — Kilmer's Legend — 22 districts · the alibi
WHAT  — The record as religion and as alibi: the winning that makes the town worship him and makes his abuse untouchable.
WHERE — VBL · Varsity Blues (1999)  Framework inputs: Varsity Blues (1999, dir. Brian Robbins, MTV Films/Paramount); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
